{"id": "idq1665702567079", "title": "websave", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "websave"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/idq1665702567079.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">websave</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: weboperation…end   \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: weboperation…end   \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gsi1665702594894.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: websetocc \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: websetocc \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pfj1665702684183.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/idq1665702567079.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/idq1665702567079.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/idq1665702567079.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528498\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528498\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104idq1665702567079.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/idq1665702567079.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/idq1665702567079.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"idq1665702567079\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">websave  \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"idq1665702567079__websave_249128\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Writes a JSON stream from the data in a component to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$webinfo(\"data\")</span>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"idq1665702567079__topic_d79607e1_d79608e1_d79609e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"idq1665702567079__codeblock_css_3mz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">websave{/mod | /one}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__section_N10044_N10024_N10001\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79613e1_d79614e1_d79615e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">websave</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__topic_d52372e1_d52373e1_d52374e1_d52375e1_d52376e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e78\">Qualifiers</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/mod</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1__entry__2\">Includes only modified occurrences in the JSON\n                        stream.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/one</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7847e1_d7848e1_d7849e1__entry__2\">Includes only current outer occurrence (with\n                        all inner occurrences) in the JSON stream.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__topic_d52377e1_d52378e1_d52379e1_d52380e1_d52381e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e136\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79622e1_d79623e1_d79624e1\">The output of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websave</span> includes the\n            CRC, ID, and STATUS for every occurrence and is put in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$webinfo</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(\"data\")</code> channel. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dvf1665702566367.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dvf1665702566367.html#dvf1665702566367__topic_d28412e1_d28413e1_d28414e1_d28415e1_d28416e1\">Metadata for Reconnect</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__1\"> &lt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__2\">Success</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"idq1665702567079__table_d7850e1_d7851e1_d7852e1__entry__2\">Number of images for which a temporary file\n                        could not be created.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__section_x5q_gct_q1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e219\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use in Dynamic Server Page components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__topic_d52387e1_d52388e1_d52389e1_d52390e1_d52391e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e228\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79634e1_d79635e1_d79636e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websave</span> statement creates a JSON stream from the data in a component. The stream is built from the complete hitlist, including occurrences currently marked for deletion. Occurrences and fields are selected from the data set based on switches used by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websave</span> statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79637e1_d79638e1_d79639e1\">The entities and fields included in the stream are defined by the component structure, so both database and non-database fields are included in the JSON stream.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79640e1_d79641e1_d79642e1\">You can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$JSON_INDENT</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$JSON_SHOWNAMES</span> assignment settings to make the JSON stream more human-readable for development and debugging purposes.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__topic_d52392e1_d52393e1_d52394e1_d52395e1_d52396e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e255\">Triggers Fired by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websave</span>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79646e1_d79647e1_d79648e1\">The following triggers are fired by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websave</span> statement and can be used to customize the process of saving a component into an JSON stream:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"idq1665702567079__li_d33548e1_d33549e1_d33550e1\">preSerialize—fired immediately before an\n               occurrence is saved from a component into a disconnected record set. The occurrence\n               is available and can be examined. For example, an occurrence can be excluded from the\n               save, or the value for a derived field can be calculated. See the \"trigger\n               preSerialize topic\".</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"idq1665702567079__li_d33551e1_d33552e1_d33553e1\">postSerialize—fired immediately after an\n               occurrence is saved from a component into a disconnected record set. See the \"trigger\n               postSerialize topic\".</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__topic_d52397e1_d52398e1_d52399e1_d52400e1_d52401e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e279\">Images</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"idq1665702567079__p_d79652e1_d79653e1_d79654e1\">When the component contains images from a database, the Uniface Server creates temporary image files in the project directory. If it does not have write privileges for the project directory, this action fails. The page is still presented to the browser, but with image load error icons in the locations of the images.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"idq1665702567079__section_alp_2vq_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d98541e288\">Example: <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">websave</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following code creates a JSON stream from a component's data\n            structure and writes the result to the message frame.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104idq1665702567079_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"idq1665702567079__codeblock_axx_kmz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">clear\nretrieve/e \"ORDER.INOUTER\"\nwebsave\nputmess $webinfo(\"data\")\nreturn\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pnu1665702566114.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger preSerialize</a><p>System trigger that processes an occurrence before it is saved from a component into a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cxh1665702566923.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger postSerialize</a><p>System trigger that processes an occurrence after it is saved from a component into a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jbl1665702567156.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>JSON</a><p>The JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) is a data-interchange format based on a subset of JavaScript. It provides an alternative to XML and is often used for serializing and transmitting structured data over a network connection, especially in web applications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ads1665702700197.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$JSON_INDENT</a><p>Format JSON output with indents to make it more readable.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vld1665702700267.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$JSON_SHOWNAMES</a><p>Show fully qualified names in JSON streams as extra attributes of fields and entities.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fyu1665702539304.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$webinfo</a><p>Return or set information about the current HTTP request or response.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528498\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528498\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "websave Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 websave Writes a JSON stream from the data in a component to $webinfo(\"data\") . websave{/mod | /one} Copy Example: websave Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /mod Includes only modified occurrences in the JSON stream. /one Includes only current outer occurrence (with all inner occurrences) in the JSON stream. Return Values The output of websave includes the CRC, ID, and STATUS for every occurrence and is put in the $webinfo (\"data\") channel. For more information, see Metadata for Reconnect . Table 2. Values returned in $status Value Meaning <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. 0 Success >0 Number of images for which a temporary file could not be created. Use Use in Dynamic Server Page components. Description The websave statement creates a JSON stream from the data in a component. The stream is built from the complete hitlist, including occurrences currently marked for deletion. Occurrences and fields are selected from the data set based on switches used by the websave statement. The entities and fields included in the stream are defined by the component structure, so both database and non-database fields are included in the JSON stream. You can use the $JSON_INDENT and $JSON_SHOWNAMES assignment settings to make the JSON stream more human-readable for development and debugging purposes. Triggers Fired by websave The following triggers are fired by the websave statement and can be used to customize the process of saving a component into an JSON stream: preSerialize—fired immediately before an occurrence is saved from a component into a disconnected record set. The occurrence is available and can be examined. For example, an occurrence can be excluded from the save, or the value for a derived field can be calculated. See the \"trigger preSerialize topic\". postSerialize—fired immediately after an occurrence is saved from a component into a disconnected record set. See the \"trigger postSerialize topic\". Images When the component contains images from a database, the Uniface Server creates temporary image files in the project directory. If it does not have write privileges for the project directory, this action fails. The page is still presented to the browser, but with image load error icons in the locations of the images. Example: websave The following code creates a JSON stream from a component's data structure and writes the result to the message frame. Explain this code clear retrieve/e \"ORDER.INOUTER\" websave putmess $webinfo(\"data\") return Copy Related Links trigger preSerialize System trigger that processes an occurrence before it is saved from a component into a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct). trigger postSerialize System trigger that processes an occurrence after it is saved from a component into a disconnected record set (XML, JSON, or Struct). JSON The JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) is a data-interchange format based on a subset of JavaScript. It provides an alternative to XML and is often used for serializing and transmitting structured data over a network connection, especially in web applications. $JSON_INDENT Format JSON output with indents to make it more readable. $JSON_SHOWNAMES Show fully qualified names in JSON streams as extra attributes of fields and entities. $webinfo Return or set information about the current HTTP request or response. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}